<i>Wizard</i></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ubaedm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Baedm</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0> at: 8/15/01 1:27:22 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ueindyinromenril.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eindyin Romenril</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 2:35:25 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://eindyin.homestead.com/files/einphoto.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tishan's Kilt</span><hr size=1> I sat in LFay for around half an hour killing shadowed men.  I tried givin them the two weaps but they alway aggroed on me at 52 sooooo.. I got a 54 Troll Shaman to give em to em, and I got the ball straight away.  Worked wonderfully <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
As for the Shinta frog, when I went there he wasn't up and a Shin warrior was in his place.  I'm amiable to Frogs, and the Shin dropped in one shot and nothin else aggroed.  15mins later the Shinta popped, dropped in an IC and I was off to get my kilt.  Hehe I only got this on the weeked by the way, and at 52 also.. *hangs head*.  Took me about 2 hrs doing the whole thing.  <br>
No graphic on High Elves for sure. <p><Font color=red>Eindyin Romenril<br>
High Elf Channeler of the 52nd nerf<br>
Ayonae Ro server</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvermil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vermil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/20/01 3:15:44 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tishan's Kilt</span><hr size=1> Wow, a major bump - hehehe. But, for those of you that may be still after the Shadowed Ball (5AC, No Rent), the 'giveing of shadow wepons' works every time. I know - we tried it a lot last night while looking for my Patch of Shadow (I'm 5 points smarter now, Thankyou! )<br>
<br>
In wolf form (helps to have a druid, hehehe) give the snowcone holding shadowmen shadow weapons until the snowcone is no longer visible. <br>
<br>
Kill the shadow man. loot the body. The cone is there - guarenteed.<br>
<br>
This also works for the book of shadow (I think thats its name) for the Necro quest - Words of Darkness or somthing. The Necro shadowmen hold this book - give them weps and kill them, bingo! one book on the corpse.<br>
<br>
Works everytime. <p>Vermil Darkmire<BR>

